text: Tracy Beaker Returns is a British television series for children starring Dani Harmer. It was first broadcast on 8 January 2010, on CBBC and BBC HD. It won the BAFTA award. It was replaced by a new series called The Dumping Ground in 2013. ==References== ==Other websites== * * * Category:BBC Television programmes Category:Children's television series Category:BAFTA Award winning programmes
